{"tid":359218,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【恐怖車禍】河源貨車直撞廣場舞大媽 釀3死7傷司機被捕","createTime":"2017-08-14T10:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T11:08:32.000Z","uid":36607,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46e07d7bc63df1d48abfb72ccc743b24e9b816e6","tid":359218,"uid":36607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:28:32.000Z","msg":"廣東河源昨晚發生嚴重車禍，一部貨車失控，撞上一群跳完廣場舞、結伴回家的大媽們，造成3死7傷。司機已經被當局拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n事發昨晚9時許，一架從江西開往廣東揭陽的貨車，駛至河源市省道339線和平縣路段時，突然失控，撞向路邊，這時正有一群跳完廣場舞、正在結伴回家的大媽的隊伍。消息指當時大媽們驚慌尖叫，不斷逃跑。<br />\n<br />\n當局接報後召來大批救護車到場搶救，2人當場死亡，8名傷者送院搶救，其中一人傷重不治，一人危殆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170814&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57080405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170814%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57080405&d=eILJjGo7kX%2BklWE%2BFO9zcqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=a7a8bcd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170814%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57080405&h=1c35c99d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170814&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57080405</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人講勇武，真係無得同支那比<br />\n口德村村民ready? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d17fc0027ab37fdd5ad9ee021a5b5f6c7198397","tid":359218,"uid":116530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"撞得好 撞得妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69726bd97d7c2ec8c23953a0385a73e66b77ae6d","tid":359218,"uid":116530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撞得好 撞得妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撞到呱呱叫"},{"pid":"21b347fadec92b204f0099ec5f9b6bab21f4ffab","tid":359218,"uid":36029,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T10:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.